ten 
<bibRefCitation author="Hove, H. A. ten &amp; Zibrowius, H." box="[562,829,573,596]" pageId="58" pageNumber="59" pagination="21 - 31" refId="ref61673" refString="Hove, H. A. ten &amp; Zibrowius, H. (1986) Laminatubus alvini gen. et sp. n. and Protis hydrothermica sp. n. (Polychaeta, Serpulidae) from the bathyal hydrothermal vent communities in the eastern Pacific. Zoologica Scripta, 15, 21 - 31." type="journal article" year="1986">Hove &amp; Zibrowius, 1986</bibRefCitation>
